Sentencas: Potential of BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-delta (BZCY) electrolyte prepared by ammonium carbonate coprecipitation was investigated for application in solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Evaluation of BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3-δ electrolyte prepared by carbonate precipitation for a mixed ion-conducting SOFC

Sentencas: An 8 mu m thick BZCY electrolyte layer was deposited on a porous Ni-BZCY anode.

Sentencas: A slurry mixture of BZCY-LaSr3Co1.5Fe1.5O10-delta (LSCF) was used as the cathode.
